snippet.title: ARSONATE - Outwit the HOST in a death game where fire spreads with each flip of a card!
snippet.description:
Play the demo on itch.io https://nashset.itch.io/arsonate-demo?ac=qfCyYFQF-yt Locked in a FIRE TOWER.

A FOREST FIRE spreads with each flip of a card.

Use UTILITIES to outwit the [HOST].

Be the LAST tower standing.

Do you fear DEATH?
